column5: Wondering if anybody has been to this camp at sioux lookout. they are advertising for jobs right now, and I'm interested in what type of camp it is. Any opinions?
Never been there, Looks nice, i here lots of good things about it, I have fishe the Sioux Lookout area and it is excellent!
